They Call Me Lucky (1973 - South Africa)

Western
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1764707/


This movie is a sequel to Three Bullets for a Long Gun 1971

Lucky's band of outlaws holds a rich girl for ransom and plans a new series of robberies. Meanwhile, a peasant who was widowed by one of Lucky's men teams up with a bounty hunter to plot a premature end to Lucky's lucky streak.
